title: The Elder Scrolls V Skyrim Legendary Edition
description:
Before you play,I would like to say something.
Skyrim is a wonderful game.I have spent hours upon hours playing it and I have loved it.

I started off with a pirated copy and then I bought the legit version.
I implore you to do the same.Get this for trying it out but please do support Bethesda by actually buying the game.They are a great company and they deserve it.Plus they have brilliant customer service.
May people realize that p2p is not all bad.Prove them wrong.Show that it promotes the industry too.
That is all. Please enjoy :)


This is my Skyrim Ultimate Collection Pack.
Its Contents are as follows:

The Legendary Edition with all DLC.
Updated to the final Build.
Collector's Edition Scans.
DVD Covers.
Collector's Edition Cloth Map Scans.
Ultimate Edition DVD Scans.
The Elder Scrolls V Skyrim - Artbook.
Elder Scrolls V - Skyrim The Official Game Guide.
The Infernal City An Elder Scrolls Novel.
Behind The Wall:The Making Of Skyrim.
Behind The Scenes And Interview With Cast And Crew.
The Skyrim Official Game Soundtrack.
The Best Skyrim Wallpaper Packs I've found till date.
Bonus Videos at 1080p

Cheers :)
Ron~
